{"tid":2290582,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"英國將禁售汽柴油車時間提前5年至2030年","createTime":"2020-11-18T06:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T10:33:28.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"24cd4c3c9b082f88ca2b7c8b8de4814979be0df7","tid":2290582,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:09:28.000Z","msg":"英國政府於當地時間11月17日宣佈，到2030年前禁止銷售汽油車和柴油車新車。作為應對氣候變化的核心措施，推動不直接排放溫室氣體的純電動汽車（EV）普及。美國及加拿大等國也相繼宣佈禁售汽油車，純電動汽車將在全球加速普及。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nikkei.com/industry/icar/42795-2020-11-18-11-12-34.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nikkei.com%2Findustry%2Ficar%2F42795-2020-11-18-11-12-34.html&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1W58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=88088c8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nikkei.com/industry/icar/42795-2020-11-18-11-12-34.html</a>"},{"pid":"7803effded38d7593bce4223cf0197604e46b9fb","tid":2290582,"uid":110864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"三傻又升"},{"pid":"2036c37e0164803775285530194f84d7d1f846da","tid":2290582,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"計唔計搵食車先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲貨車點算 都未有取代品"},{"pid":"65048a51c3f848870195a9fe9bc32d35deb4b366","tid":2290582,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:11:58.000Z","msg":"到時要資助d 人換車又要印錢"},{"pid":"02ec00f0c615c7b08a7db7eb0185280af398a022","tid":2290582,"uid":29218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2036c37e0164803775285530194f84d7d1f846da","tid":2290582,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"計唔計搵食車先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲貨車點算 都未有取代品"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:12:32.000Z","msg":"唔畀賣啫<br />\n可以照用"},{"pid":"ef07b64383cf3c938e85f94bdecc6f47af035ef5","tid":2290582,"uid":72831,"li